19
00:03:48,690 --> 00:03:55,340
[Archives: The Nanyang Mystery]

20
00:03:55,630 --> 00:03:58,240
[Episode 7]

21
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:18,570
You're just a cripple.

22
00:05:19,540 --> 00:05:21,070
When did you know

23
00:05:21,650 --> 00:05:23,230
