48
00:07:15,590 --> 00:07:16,720
You are not a burden.

49
00:07:16,810 --> 00:07:17,940
You are not a burden.

50
00:07:18,450 --> 00:07:21,020
Stop messing around. You'll die here.

51
00:07:21,310 --> 00:07:22,190
