54
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:33,390
You are my brother.

55
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:34,690
You must stay alive.

56
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,480
Stay alive!

57
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,500
