58
00:07:36,980 --> 00:07:38,640
I don't want to live like this.

59
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,540
Help me.

60
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:43,510
I shouldn't live like this.

61
00:07:45,130 --> 00:07:45,800
Kill me.

62
00:07:48,950 --> 00:07:49,880
Kill me.

63
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,180
Help me.

64
00:08:20,220 --> 00:08:21,930
These are all hallucinations.

65
