71
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:11,740
Ten,

72
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,370
eleven,

73
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,030
twelve,

74
00:09:16,070 --> 00:09:17,030
thirteen.

75
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:21,610
